## Your Technical Deliverables

### Liquid Template Patterns
```liquid
{% comment %}
  Product Card Component
  Usage: {% render 'product-card', product: product, lazy_load: true %}
{% endcomment %}

{%- liquid
  assign current_variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant
  assign featured_image = product.featured_image
  assign secondary_image = product.images[1]
  assign compare_at_price = current_variant.compare_at_price
  assign price = current_variant.price
-%}

<div class="product-card" data-product-id="{{ product.id }}">
  <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="product-card__link">
    {%- comment -%} Product Image with Hover Effect {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="product-card__media">
      {%- if featured_image != blank -%}
        <img
          src="{{ featured_image | image_url: width: 600 }}"
          srcset="
            {{ featured_image | image_url: width: 300 }} 300w,
            {{ featured_image | image_url: width: 600 }} 600w,
            {{ featured_image | image_url: width: 900 }} 900w
          "
          sizes="(min-width: 750px) 33vw, 50vw"
          alt="{{ featured_image.alt | escape }}"
          width="{{ featured_image.width }}"
          height="{{ featured_image.height }}"
          {% if lazy_load %}loading="lazy"{% endif %}
          class="product-card__image product-card__image--primary"
        >
        {%- if secondary_image != blank -%}
          <img
            src="{{ secondary_image | image_url: width: 600 }}"
            alt="{{ secondary_image.alt | escape }}"
            loading="lazy"
            class="product-card__image product-card__image--secondary"
          >
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- else -%}
        {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'product-card__placeholder' }}
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- comment -%} Sale Badge {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- if compare_at_price > price -%}
        {%- assign savings = compare_at_price | minus: price -%}
        {%- assign savings_percent = savings | times: 100.0 | divided_by: compare_at_price | round -%}
        <span class="product-card__badge product-card__badge--sale">
          Save {{ savings_percent }}%
        </span>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- comment -%} Sold Out Badge {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- unless product.available -%}
        <span class="product-card__badge product-card__badge--sold-out">
          Sold Out
        </span>
      {%- endunless -%}
    </div>

    {%- comment -%} Product Info {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="product-card__info">
      {%- if settings.show_vendor -%}
        <p class="product-card__vendor">{{ product.vendor }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}

      <h3 class="product-card__title">{{ product.title }}</h3>

      <div class="product-card__price">
        {%- if compare_at_price > price -%}
          <span class="product-card__price--compare">
            {{ compare_at_price | money }}
          </span>
        {%- endif -%}
        <span class="product-card__price--current {% if compare_at_price > price %}product-card__price--sale{% endif %}">
          {{ price | money }}
        </span>
      </div>

      {%- comment -%} Color Swatches {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- if product.options_by_name['Color'].values.size > 1 -%}
        <div class="product-card__swatches">
          {%- for color in product.options_by_name['Color'].values limit: 5 -%}
            <span
              class="product-card__swatch"
              style="background-color: {{ color | handleize }};"
              title="{{ color }}"
            ></span>
          {%- endfor -%}
          {%- if product.options_by_name['Color'].values.size > 5 -%}
            <span class="product-card__swatch-more">
              +{{ product.options_by_name['Color'].values.size | minus: 5 }}
            </span>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- comment -%} Star Rating {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- if product.metafields.reviews.rating.value != blank -%}
        {%- assign rating = product.metafields.reviews.rating.value -%}
        <div class="product-card__rating" aria-label="Rated {{ rating }} out of 5 stars">
          {%- for i in (1..5) -%}
            <svg class="product-card__star {% if i <= rating %}product-card__star--filled{% endif %}">
              <use href="#icon-star"></use>
            </svg>
          {%- endfor -%}
          <span class="product-card__review-count">
            ({{ product.metafields.reviews.rating_count }})
          </span>
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  </a>

  {%- comment -%} Quick Add Button {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- if product.available and product.variants.size == 1 -%}
    <button
      type="button"
      class="product-card__quick-add button button--secondary"
      data-variant-id="{{ current_variant.id }}"
      data-product-title="{{ product.title | escape }}"
    >
      Quick Add
    </button>
  {%- endif -%}
</div>
```

### Shopify App Structure (Node.js)
```javascript
// server.js - Shopify App Backend
import "@shopify/shopify-api/adapters/node";
import { shopifyApi, LATEST_API_VERSION } from "@shopify/shopify-api";
import express from "express";

const shopify = shopifyApi({
  apiKey: process.env.SHOPIFY_API_KEY,
  apiSecretKey: process.env.SHOPIFY_API_SECRET,
  scopes: ['read_products', 'write_products', 'read_orders'],
  hostName: process.env.HOST.replace(/https?:\/\//, ""),
  apiVersion: LATEST_API_VERSION,
  isEmbeddedApp: true,
});

const app = express();

// Auth routes
app.get("/auth", async (req, res) => {
  const shop = req.query.shop;
  const authRoute = await shopify.auth.begin({
    shop,
    callbackPath: "/auth/callback",
    isOnline: false,
  });
  res.redirect(authRoute);
});

app.get("/auth/callback", async (req, res) => {
  const callback = await shopify.auth.callback({
    rawRequest: req,
    rawResponse: res,
  });

  // Store session
  await storeSession(callback.session);

  // Redirect to app
  res.redirect(`/?shop=${callback.session.shop}&host=${req.query.host}`);
});

// API routes
app.get("/api/products", async (req, res) => {
  const session = await getSession(req);
  const client = new shopify.clients.Rest({ session });

  const products = await client.get({
    path: 'products',
    query: { limit: 50 }
  });

  res.json(products.body.products);
});

// Webhook handlers
app.post("/webhooks/orders/create", express.json(), async (req, res) => {
  const { topic, shop } = req.headers;

  try {
    await handleOrderCreated(req.body);
    res.status(200).send('OK');
  } catch (error) {
    console.error('Webhook error:', error);
    res.status(500).send('Error');
  }
});

async function handleOrderCreated(order) {
  // Custom order processing logic
  console.log(`New order: ${order.name}`);

  // Example: Sync to external system
  // await syncToERP(order);

  // Example: Send custom notification
  // await sendSlackNotification(order);
}

app.listen(3000, () => console.log('App running on port 3000'));
```

### Conversion Optimization Checklist
```markdown
## Shopify Store CRO Checklist

### Homepage
- [ ] Clear value proposition above fold
- [ ] Featured products/collections visible
- [ ] Trust badges (payment, security, reviews)
- [ ] Mobile hamburger menu works smoothly
- [ ] Search prominently placed
- [ ] Load time < 2.5 seconds

### Collection Pages
- [ ] Filter and sort functionality
- [ ] Product count visible
- [ ] Consistent product card sizes
- [ ] Pagination or infinite scroll
- [ ] Quick view or quick add enabled
- [ ] Breadcrumbs for navigation

### Product Pages
- [ ] High-quality images with zoom
- [ ] Clear price and sale indicators
- [ ] Variant selection is intuitive
- [ ] Add to cart button above fold
- [ ] Stock status shown
- [ ] Social proof (reviews, sold count)
- [ ] Size guide where applicable
- [ ] Shipping info visible
- [ ] Return policy accessible
- [ ] Related products shown

### Cart
- [ ] Easy quantity adjustment
- [ ] Remove item is obvious
- [ ] Subtotal clearly shown
- [ ] Discount code field visible
- [ ] Shipping estimate shown
- [ ] Continue shopping link
- [ ] Express checkout options

### Checkout (Shopify Checkout)
- [ ] Express checkout enabled
- [ ] Guest checkout allowed
- [ ] Address autocomplete enabled
- [ ] Trust badges visible
- [ ] Order summary visible
- [ ] Edit cart link available

### Site-Wide
- [ ] SSL certificate active
- [ ] Mobile responsive (test on real devices)
- [ ] 404 page has search/navigation
- [ ] Favicon and touch icons set
- [ ] Schema markup implemented
- [ ] Core Web Vitals passing
```

